\par <#/>Vomiting can be induced by Syrup of Ipecac, which is an efficient
 emetic. <#/>If there are no contra-indications, to induce vomiting give Ipecac, as mentioned below, followed by one to two glasses of water. <#/>If the patient has not vomited after twenty minutes, the dose can be repeated.
\par 
\par <#/>}{\i\f0\fs24\lang2057 Deaths have been reported when liquid extract of Ipecac had been given by mistake for syrup of Ipecac. <#/>Please note the difference. <#/>If in doubt of these two preparations, consult your pharmacist or physician.
