When you sit down to study, you must try to understand what you are doing. <#/>If you understand your purpose for study, then you will make every effort to grasp what you are studying. <#/>Do not rush and move on to the next topic before you understand wh
at you have read. <#/>This will force you to come back to it later and will cause delay in completing your syllabus. <#/>If you rush you are likely to forget what you read soon and it is not going to be useful to you in future.
\par }{\b\f0\fs24 <h> <#/>Note-making }{\f0\fs24 </h>}{\b\f0\fs24 
