\par <#/>It is for you, Mr. Small Businessman, that we have written this guide 'EFFECTIVE SMALL BUSINESS MANAGEMENT'. <#/>You may be technically very efficient in your product
 or service speciality yet the success of your business depends on how effectively you are able to manage your business. <#/>Effective business management requires the practice of quite a number of principles and precepts. <#/>It also needs the acceptance
 of professional ideas.
