\par <#/> Business promotion means to do everything that will help to get sales. <#/>Promotion is necessary for any business, especially small business. <#/>It is necessary to get back with a profit what you have invested - money and labour - as quickly as pos
sible.
\par <#/> Promotion helps people to know what you have for sale, and why they should buy your goods or services in preference to those of competitors. <#/>You can do a number of things to promote your business:-
